문항#According to Wilson’s Business Manual, the key to ____ your staff happy is making sure they are not overworked and always feel appreciated.
(A) taking
(B) helping
(C) encouraging
(D) keeping
답#(D)
주석#____ [your staff] [happy] 따라서 5형식 동사가 와야 한다.
Keep A B : A를 B한 상태로 만들다(유지하다.)
5형식 동사 : make, keep, leave, find, consider, (call, name, appoint, select, elect)
Encourage A (3V) A의 기운을 북돋우다.

